messages.content: Mamizou is chilling here, thinking about Vulpe! She wants to know where she has been ever since she left the forest. Shes annoyed that the Saké mun existed. She deserves Vulpe not him!!!
Veteris was Slav squatting on a rock near the shore, looking passively at the sea and the sunset. Not bothering to take in the rest of his surroundings

She noticed him and grinned a bit. She had seen him with Sanguis a few times. He MUST know stuff about Sanguis. She hopped up and walked over. "Yuhuuu~! Hello mister I have a few questions for you about the Saké mun!" She hummed once by him. Her tail was swaying a bit as she rocked on her heels
“Eh...? Who are you?” He looked over to this strange mun, raising an eyebrow in suspicion, “Saké? Isn’t that...an alcohol or something...?”
"His mun name is Sanguis I believe! Immmm Mamizou! A Tanuki! Im looking for my dear Vulpe!" She giggled

“Uh, hello then? I’m Veteris....?” He shrugs, even though she told him her name, he probably won’t remember it, she doesn’t seem like she’ll be important in his life. 
“Vulpe? Oh yeah....that fox chick...”
"So! Tell me what you know about him! Anything will do~! I want to figure out how to win Vulpe back! After all we are destined to be together!!!" She stared at him with a grin, tail wagging a bit
“And why should I tell shit? I barely know you.” He sighs, “Also, a bit of advice, destiny is bullcrap, if you keep following some make-believe entity........you’ll surely hit an impassable obstacle”

She pouted a bit "Booooo! Youre no fun!" She takes something out of her pocket and grins, tail wagging more now. She blows it on him and....hes a pit bull now....or something similar to that. She really doesnt care.. this is funny to her
At first the change suprised him, though he then becomes very unamused, his new ears twitching in irritation, giving a growl.
She snickered "Awww is the wittwe puppy wuppy maddddd~?"

Veteris really wanted to bite this wack job and go home, but then again he liked his mun body, so for the moment, he retracts his jaws, and yawns, curling up on the stone, facing away from Mamizou, starts to doze off

She blinked. Well he wasn't any fun. She would just have to try and annoy him more then! She hummed a bit "Hey hey heyyyyy Ill leave you alone if you tell me about Sanguis~ Otherwise Ill keep bugging you!!!" She nudged him with her shoe, huffing a bit "Or are you too lazy~"

He growls, can’t this girl just buzz off? His head turns around giving a *you think I can talk like this??* look, his tail swatting at her shoe, this was worst than his first reaping mission, and at least back then he didn’t get turned into a **Dog** of all things..
"Kehehehe! The wittwe puppy wuppy cant tawk!!" She snapped her fingers and let him go back into his mun form before trying to kick him

He groans, slowly shifting back up, though his eyes narrow to slits as he intercepts the upcoming kick, grabbing her leg harshly
, “**Don’t**” 
was all he uttered before rising back up, the threatening aura lasting for a bit then reverting back to his ‘I could care less’ attitude “Besides, I know dick about him, and I lived with him for a while, the most is that he looks like an edge lord and has a magic sword, *thats it*” he exasperatedly exclaims, oh and the Replicas but....she probably won’t be able to understand that anyway.
She yelped, tail fluffing up a bit. "Hmph. Youre boring. Ill just need to find Vulpe myself then and take her back! After all shes _mine_."
He grumbled, though....her last words....reminded him of someone....he quickly looked away to the sea, “Well good luck, from what I could tell, Vulpes stubborn when it comes to Sanguis.....”
"She wont be when Im through with her~" She giggled starting to walk off "Or through with him...Whatever works Ill get her back." She sorta mumbled those last parts
*why did he have a bad feeling about this?*

- - - -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- - - -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- - - -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- 
the portal reopened as Repluis rolled out, laying on the sand. “Ughhh....” *that was close*
_Repluis we should hide. The main part of us has been captured._ The goop sounded scared
*got it. Don’t worry, I won’t give you up till I bleed my last drop of blood!*. He looks around for a good hiding place, maybe a cave or......something else.

_Thank you....We are.....glad your our friend...._ 

There was a cave out in the distance!

*right back at you!*
He quickly jogged to the entrance, taking a peek in
It was empty! How lucky!!!

Wow! No monsters or anything! Great! 
He scurried inside and took a seat down
*We’ll stay here in till it’s safe!*

_Good idea!_ The goop hummed _Also....We have decided on a look....that we will call our own._ it dissolved its form in the mindscale before reforming with a new look. Alot more solid looking! Just with goopy legs!
*oooohh!* he claps his hands a little *amazing!*
_Thank you!!!_ they smiled, new tail wagging happily
Vulpe is here now! She sighs a bit as she walks along the sandy beach, trying to find Repluis
Meanwhile a certain siren was watching from the water. She grinned upon seeing Vulpe. This would be fun
Kēnā licked her lips. This should be an easy meal for her~
*oh shit I hear somebody....wait it’s vulpe* he, slowly stays close to a wall of the cave

She sat on the bench, looking out over the water. She sighed but stood up on edge when she heard singing. However....she soon relaxed "Pretty......" She mumbled

Kēnā had begun to sing

His ear twitched in confusion, moving closer to the entrance 
*somethings wrong*
Vulpe began to walk towards the water, under the spell of the siren song
Panic rushed through his system, this isn’t right, somethings wrong, gotta save Kitty, gotta save kitty......but his friend.....Repluis’s eyes started to warp...

Vulpe was getting closer and closer to the water.

Kēnā kept singing. She could easily be seen from the cave.

*you know what.....fuck it, nobody’s gonna hurt* **My kitty** 
A snarl escapes as he books it out and clutches Vulpes waist tight, digging his feet in the sand

Kēnā saw this and growled a bit, before trying to make him fall under her spell as well

Vulpe struggled to get out of his grip and walk to her doom "So....pretty....." She mumbled

He growled a bit back, the song only making his ear twitch violently, 
Seeing that Vulpe was still under the spell, he bites down on her neck, making direct eye contact with Kēnā, with narrowed eyes@

Vulpes eyes widened and she yelps, snapping out of the spell. "OW!!!!!" She hissed, turning around to see Repluis. "What was that for?!"

Kēnā let out a 'tsk' and gave up, diving back under the water
“I saved you! That thing was gonna eat you and somebody had to make you snap out of it!” He pouted
She blinked "Ah- A siren....I....cant belive I fell under her spell....This.....hasnt happened before...." She frowned a bit "But....thank you for saving me...."
She seemed upset for falling under the spell....Her leg was glowing a bit and she shifted her weight onto her non cracked leg
_Repluis are you sure being this ckose to her is safe?_

“Hmph! Your welcome!” He grins, before noticing the leg “Your leg...” he frowns
*yes, she hasn’t done anything yet, so*

"Ill be fine....Its nothing I can't handle....Just....Kinda upset that I fell under the sirens spell so easily....I have strong mental barriers.....This....is unusual...." she sighed, gently hugging him.
She knew it wasnt Sanguis in control but right now she...didnt care. She just needed a hug.
Repluis quickly returned the hug, humming quietly

She purred a bit, just staying in the hug before eventually shifting her weight to be more even as her leg stopped glowing. "Mmmm see? What did I tell you? Ill be fine..." She purred a bit, gently cupping his face. It was now or never......She had to do this. "Sorry." She concentrated and she seems to....phase into him? She was using her ability to possess others.
He smiled but it quickly turned into a hurt expression , as he felt his consciousness slip away
Vulpe sat down to make it more comfortable before going into his mindscape.
Vulpe wakes up and groans "Ughhh....I forgot how draining it is to possess someone...."
She looks over at Sanguis, worried that she might of hurt him when possessing him...
She hears a muffled “I’m alright,” as Sanguis lifts his face from the sand, a sheepish smile plastered on, “heh....I’m....definitely taking a shower after this....”
She chuckled, standing up a little wobbly, and offering a hand out to him "Cmon, lets head back to the temple."
Shes a bit unsteady on her feet
Stumbling back up, he holds onto her shoulder, “You can use me as a crutch. Ok?”
She nodded a bit "Alright...." She smooches his cheek
"Lets...get going then..." She and a small smile on her face
“Mhm....” a bright orange tinted his cheeks, and he clutched her waist, for stability.
Her tails had a slight wag at that. Off the 2 go to the temple!
Helio is vibing here making a sand castle. Hes very content
Shale splashes out of the water like a not so graceful mermaid. "What's up?" She grins.
Helio yelps a bit, suprised "O-Oh!!! Hi Shale!" He waves
"Hello, Helio." She flicks water at him with her tail.
He laughs a bit "Im makinf a sandcastle!!" Oh wow hes good at it. Its actually big
"Good job. I'm diving for fish." She gestures.
"Careful, I heard that sirens live in these waters...."
"You mean the pretty girl ones? Doesn't bother me." She grins.
He smiled "Well thats good. How are your wifes??"
"Fabulous and beautiful." She snorts.
"Thats good to hear!!!" Helios tail wagged a bit
She grins at him. "So what've you been doing?"
"Ive just been relaxing!!! Its nice just vibing with the many pets i have."
"Any romances I should know about? Do you have the Gossips™️?"
"Hmm no romances that I know of." He hummed
"Aw. Anything else?" She kicks her legs, splashing in the waves. "You should come in, it's nice."
"...I.....dont know how to swim....." He played with his hands a bit
"Bro." She outstretches a hand. "C'mere, I'll teach you."
He walked over, very nervous
"I'm not gonna eat you, and neither is the ocean. Any of your clothes super heavy?"
He shook his head "No..."
"Right, then come in! Water's nice." She flips onto her back, splashing.
He walks into the water, nervous about it
"Now go up to your chest or something."
He nodded and did so
"Okay, now push off and try keep afloat."
"H-how??"
"Spread your arms, and keep still. Don't flail." She demonstrates, vibing on her back. "Kick your legs slowly."
He nodded and tried to do so
"Good job. From here on it's just doing that and waving your legs at the same time."
"A-alright..."
"Try just kicking your legs somewhat." She propels herself forward.
He tried to kick his legs
"Don't flounder, just gently." She advises, swimming circles around him. "Use your tail if ya want."
He nodded and began to use his tail to help him swim
"Good job." She dives down and scrabbles before bringing up a slice of rock. "Look, it's me." She jokes.
Vulpe is here to kinda try and get over her fear of water and also chill with her husband. Shes lounging in her kitsune form where the water cant reach her. At least its nice and warm!
Shes just laying on her back, enjoying the warmth
A pair of arms wrap around her fluffy neck, “mmm, so comfy~” a muffled voice called out, it was not Sanguis’s but it was familiar

She purred a bit "Mmm Hello Rep~" She knew he was the only other mun who would wrap his arms around her like that. He was really the only one allowed to do so. She didnt mind that it was Rep, It would be nice to spend time with him too. She nuzzled into him, tails wagging
